sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Restaurant Owner or Operations User
    participant UI as KhanaBook Interface
    participant KB as KhanaBook Backend
    participant EB as Easebuzz

    User->>UI: Enter OTP or request resend
    UI->>KB: Submit OTP action
    KB->>KB: Resolve tenant or approved operations context
    KB->>EB: Verify OTP or resend OTP
    EB-->>KB: Return OTP result
    KB-->>UI: Show success or correction required

